<p>
	John, Dave and, yes, Pilot Pete come together to share as much Mac knowledge as they possibly can in &#8220;just about an hour.&#8221; Moving from iOS Battery Life help to AppleScript walkthroughs, your favorite Mac Geeks have a lot to teach you this time around. Enjoy and download today, it&#39;s free!</p>
<p>
	<strong>Sponsor:</strong> <a href="http://www.barebones.com/" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">BBEdit</a>: BBEdit is the leading professional-strength HTML and text editor for the Macintosh. A text power tool for everyone!</p>
